flowchart TD
    A[Winning claim selected] --> B[Inspect user intent]
    B --> C{Shareable context?}
    C -- Yes --> D[Set disclosure to category]
    C -- No --> E{Merchant troubleshooting intent?}
    E -- Yes --> F[Set disclosure to merchant]
    E -- No --> G{Planning or goal intent?}
    G -- Yes --> D
    G -- No --> H[Set disclosure to summary]
    D --> I[Filter evidence atoms]
    F --> I
    H --> I
    I --> J[Redact disallowed fields]
    J --> K[Emit filtered evidence bundle]
